{"tid":1421583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"甲級戰犯何式凝冇交錢續牌扮社工","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:23:31.000Z","uid":101639,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17a2320d79e77e71fd84e07aaee0515273b6f701","tid":1421583,"uid":101639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"何式凝件騎呢死左膠最鐘意威威打卡扮大台同打飛機<br />\n5年前話自己走在最前線而琴日發起女權運動又想搏光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己就輕鬆走人，嗰80位天水圍巴絲就畀你過兩棟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正當啲人屌柒你條仆街影衰社福界，手痕之下去查...點知有人原來冇註冊定未續牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扮社工好似犯法㗎可？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYNOepj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYNOepj.png&h=2a962e94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zytmzpj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzytmzpj.png&h=c1f5a837&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m1xB7Kk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm1xB7Kk.png&h=3ee0984c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"679a2029190f9a68e2252813dd67cb73cddc495b","tid":1421583,"uid":101639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"85ce1a65cbf374e9d20f92fcebcafc938361a28e","tid":1421583,"uid":81134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2c7294fea335301c6e5f986c71916731f0f444a2","tid":1421583,"uid":58717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:43:00.000Z","msg":"佢係社工系教授 <br />\n但好似冇講自己係註冊社工？(如果係當場/任何場合有就當別論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nEven自己CV都無提及RSW等字眼 小心炒車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9ohTCe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9ohTCe.png&h=ecd29758&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"def3e4c6776d725f5521f40926dd2e2d908ee1c5","tid":1421583,"uid":101639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c7294fea335301c6e5f986c71916731f0f444a2","tid":1421583,"uid":58717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:43:00.000Z","msg":"佢係社工系教授 <br />\n但好似冇講自己係註冊社工？(如果係當場/任何場合有就當別論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nEven自己CV都無提及RSW等字眼 小心炒車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9ohTCe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9ohTCe.png&h=ecd29758&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打澄清<br />\n認同要搵翻條片先知有冇自稱社工 <br />\n啱啱去睇多次佢cv 佢曾經做過social work field instructor 呢個post係要supervise 學生做實習所以理論上佢之前有做過RSW <br />\n其實琴日件事好影響大家對社福界嘅睇法，大家都認為佢係社工....有社工朋友依一兩個月自己心力交瘁同時仲幫我地做情緒輔導我好感激，知道呢啲社福界左膠冇續牌去害人就更加係一件好事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzhq2JS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftzhq2JS.png&h=b6aa2246&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}